# Tal_s_Risky_Comm_Trader

## Description

The goal of this project was to create a simple e-commerce back end.

- My motivation was to make a functional e-commerce back end, given the starter code.
- I built this project to further my skills and proficiency in basic sequelize and the ORM structure.
- The main solution I strove for was to make the e-commerce back end functional and useful.
- My main learning experience from this project was how to effectively apply sequelize to an application.

## Table of Contents

- [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [Credits](#credits)
- [License](#license)

## Installation

Node.js is required to run this project.

## Usage

Use Node.js to run the e-commerce back end.
Video Walkthrough: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UfGfGwN0I74
